  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_5_18391-18463",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "18391-18463",
      "markText": "“把今天剩下的预约全部取消……不……我谁也不想见……没关系，取消。”然后他跌坐到椅子里。雪茄灭了。夜幕早已降临，他拿着熄灭的雪茄，再也没有点燃。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18391&rangeEnd=18463",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18391&rangeEnd=18463"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_3_584-679",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "584-679",
      "markText": "它们属于“如果……会……”的类型，其中的“如果……”是每个故事的基本设定，是对当今科技和文化给人类环境带来的潜在变化的假设。其可能性也许非常渺茫，也许几乎是必然，有关星际航行的故事就是如此。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=584&rangeEnd=679",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=584&rangeEnd=679"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_6_16749-16799",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "16749-16799",
      "markText": "“就是他，要不就是他的孪生兄弟吧。仔细想想，他不可能有双胞胎兄弟的，因为刚生出来就会被对方吓死了。”",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16749&rangeEnd=16799",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16749&rangeEnd=16799"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_5_14910-14994",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "14910-14994",
      "markText": "如果一个人或一家企业多年来都在以某种方式从公众那里谋取利益，那么政府和法院就有责任在将来也保护他们的利益，甚至在情况发生变化，或是与公众利益发生冲突的时候，也应这样做。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=14910&rangeEnd=14994",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=14910&rangeEnd=14994"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_24_21067-21170",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "21067-21170",
      "markText": "头顶之上，太阳在繁星点点的漆黑夜空中闪耀。而他脚下踩着的是月球的泥土。他终于站在月球上了！ 他静静地往后靠去，一阵满足感如同洪流涌遍全身，浸透了他的骨髓。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=21067&rangeEnd=21170",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=21067&rangeEnd=21170"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_6_13542-13611",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13542-13611",
      "markText": "但是，只有那些符合上层建筑利益的发明才有机会问世，其他的只会被束之高阁。你真的以为它们会让像你这样的自由人害得它们的上百亿投资打水漂吗？”",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13542&rangeEnd=13611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13542&rangeEnd=13611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_5_1042-1071",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1042-1071",
      "markText": "“如果不先移除你们脑袋中的错觉，我又怎么能植入新观点呢？”",
      "totalCount": 50,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1042&rangeEnd=1071",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1042&rangeEnd=1071"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_19_5258-5305",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "5258-5305",
      "markText": "很久以前钻石大亨们就意识到，如果钻石的货源充足，它的价值就跟玻璃没什么两样，就只有工业用途了。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5258&rangeEnd=5305",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5258&rangeEnd=5305"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_7_34628-34655",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "34628-34655",
      "markText": "此时此刻，盖恩斯真心希望自己能对精神病学有更多的了解。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=34628&rangeEnd=34655",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=34628&rangeEnd=34655"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_5_4262-4308",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4262-4308",
      "markText": "你们把这叫作‘科学学会’，依我看，只热衷于对先辈陈腐的观点抱残守缺，不如叫‘殡仪大会’算了。",
      "totalCount": 44,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4262&rangeEnd=4308",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4262&rangeEnd=4308"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_6_1356-1379",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1356-1379",
      "markText": "不看这道疤，也不看塌鼻子的话，我也算个美男子了",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1356&rangeEnd=1379",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1356&rangeEnd=1379"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_24_21696-21715",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "21696-21715",
      "markText": "他们也不在乎气密舱的外门有没有上锁了。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300092081&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=21696&rangeEnd=21715",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/daf32600813ab8a78g011c2f?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=21696&rangeEnd=21715"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300092081_5_6343-6441",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6343-6441",
      "markText": "你们或许听说过：电气工程师通过某种测量方法，在岸上就能测得横贯大洋的海底电缆确切的断裂点。我在粉色虫子的身上也能做到这一点。只要我使用仪器对这个房间内的‘横截面’进行测量，我就能指出它断裂的地方。",
